id as well.  I hope you might consider doing an independent study or experiment in the 3rd quarter to explore an aspect of science that you might like. Maybe something about scientific artists? Or relating super -string theory (physics) to knitting?!  Well done and keep up the good work in the 2nd semester!\r\nSincerely, Ms. Ashby'),(3384,2210,5,5,'2011-12-15 11:23:46','2011-12-16 06:56:31','Sem1','Mwenya:\r\n\r\n-asks questions when she is confused\r\n-often comes to class with incomplete homework\r\n-often distracts herself and others in class\r\n-needs to spend more time outside of class working on challenging concepts\r\n\r\n'),(3385,1536,NULL,2,'2011-12-15 11:24:16','2011-12-16 06:57:13','Sem1','Pandeni:\r\n\r\n-is usually prepared for class\r\n-is improving his participation\r\n\r\nNice job this semester!'),(3386,641,NULL,2,'2011-12-15 11:24:31','2011-12-16 10:25:22','Sem1','Great work Henry.  All the benchmarks are well done.  I appreciate your accurate data collection  and sustained focus during the laboratories.  Ironic that the data you collected for the test was slightly off.  Good improvement in metric conversions. I hope you will consider doing an independent study or experiment in the 3rd quarter to explore an aspect of science that you might like and further your science skills.  Keep up the good work. \r\nSincerely, Ms. Ashby'),(3387,2263,4,2,'2011-12-15 11:25:13','2011-12-16 06:57:55','Sem1','Sophi:\r\n\r\n-asks questions when she is confused\r\n-participates regularly\r\n-is sometimes unprepared without her book and/or homework\r\n\r\nNice job this semester!'),(3388,607,NULL,2,'2011-12-15 11:26:07','2011-12-16 10:22:25','Sem1','Kalkeydan is doing some excellent work in science.  I am very impressed with his graphing and interpreting graphing skills.  There are just a couple of items to bring up to standard.  I appreciate your hard working attitude and focus during labs.  Keep up the good work.  \r\nSincerely, Ms. Ashby'),(3389,714,NULL,1,'2011-12-1