d tone on his trumpet and playing with accurate pitches (especially paying attention to accidentals, the key signature and rhythms).  Once he improves in these areas, he will be able to \'graduate\' to playing \'part 1\' trumpet music.  Keep up the good work, Gen!  ','2012-03-19 13:54:58','2012-03-19 13:54:58'),(474,384,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Usually','Always','Usually','Always','','2012-03-19 14:02:50','2012-03-19 14:02:50'),(475,1629,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Usually','Usually','Always','Always','Jon has significantly improved on his trombone.  He has a fantastic tone quality and is playing more and more with rhythmic and pitch accuracy.  Continue to aim to play more difficult (or fast) rhythmic passages on your trombone with accuracy and excellent tone quality.  Keep up the great work, Jon! ','2012-03-20 05:27:00','2012-03-20 05:27:00'),(476,256,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Usually','Usually','Usually','Always','Joshua has made significant progress in his playing - especially on rhythmic passages and pitch accuracy.  He can continue to work on playing with a good tone on his saxophone and pitch accuracy (by making sure he uses the correct fingerings for the notes indicated in his music).  Keep up the good work, Joshua! ','2012-03-20 05:32:11','2012-03-20 05:32:11'),(477,1600,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Always','Always','Always','Always','Max continues to play percussion with precision, fervor and musicianship.  He is always welcome to take the initiative and play more difficult music - as a soloist or a part of an ensemble. Max can further improve on his playing by beginning to play with two or three mallets on the marimba.  Max is a fantastic musician and should keep up the excellent work! ','2012-03-20 05:45:28','2012-03-20 05:45:28'),(478,222,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Usually','Usually','Usually','Always','Kadiya continues to improve on her playing - both technically and musically.  She is playing with better tone quality and more pitch and rhythmic accuracies.  Kadiya\'s is occasionally tempted to talk with her neighbors and can be easily distracted. Despite these distractions, she is still keeping up with her homework (most of the time) and continues to do well.  Keep up the good work. ','2012-03-20 05:51:12','2012-03-20 05:51:12'),(479,1144,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Always','Always','Always','Always','Keeghan continues to improve on his saxophone playing skills - technically and musically.  He has become more helpful to other saxophonists and is solidifying his own playing by teaching others.  Keeghan can work towards playing more musically by listening to others and the overall balance.  Keep up the excellent work, Keeghan! ','2012-03-20 05:57:25','2012-03-20 05:57:25'),(480,928,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Always','Always','Always','Always','Leah continues to improve significantly on her trumpet playing skills - both musically and technically. Her obvious diligence in practicing is paying off as she leads the trumpet section completely.  Leah can continue to work on articulation her playing, tonguing and phrasing the melodic lines.  Keep up the excellent work, Leah! ','2012-03-20 06:08:38','2012-03-20 06:08:38'),(481,180,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Always','Always','Usually','Always','Liyaan continues to improve significantly on her flute playing.  Her diligence in paying attention to the pitch and rhythmic accuracies are becoming more obvious in her playing in class now.  Keep up the excellent work, Liyaan and continue to work on playing with good musical phrasing and breathing! ','2012-03-20 06:10:53','2012-03-20 06:10:53'),(482,419,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Usually','Usually','Usually','Always','Michael has a fantastic ear and demonstrated this through tuning the timpani this quarter.  He is an excellent reader and has taken extra measures to count and play difficult rhythmic passages with accuracy.  Michael can continue to work on playing more musically on the percussion and begin working on playing with two or three mallets on the keyboard percussion.  Keep up the excellent work, Michael! ','2012-03-20 06:12:43','2012-03-20 06:12:43'),(483,1237,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Usually','Always','Always','Always','Oksana continues to play with a beautiful tone quality on her flute.  She has worked hard on reading rhythmic and melodic passages with more accuracy.  Occasionally, she will be distracted with friends in the class and engage in conversation.  However, this distraction does not last too long and is quickly rectified when her section needs to play.  Overall, Oksana demonstrates proficiency in playing the flute and can challenge herself to play the pitches above the staff with better intonation and accuracy.  Keep up the excellent work, Oksana! ','2012-03-20 06:18:41','2012-03-20 06:18:41'),(484,1034,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Usually','Always','Always','Always','Ramanuj has done nothing but excel in band.  His diligence and excellent work ethic is revealed in his ability to play any song he wants on the mallet instruments.  Ramanuj plays with excellent musicianship and accuracy - both rhythmically and musically. He can challenge himself to play with two or three mallets this upcoming quarter.  Keep up the great work, Ramanuj! ','2012-03-20 06:20:58','2012-03-20 06:20:58'),(485,994,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Usually','Always','Always','Always','Rebekah continues to play clarinet with technical and musical skills.  Her diligence in practicing regularly is revealed through her excellent tone quality, playing with pitch and rhythmic accuracies and more and more, with excellent musicianship.  Rebekah\'s time on the bass clarinet was also an asset to the overall band sound as she added to the bass section.  Keep up the excellent work, Rebekah, and keep challenging yourself to play difficult passages on the clarinet!  ','2012-03-20 06:23:50','2012-03-20 06:23:50'),(486,935,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Usually','Always','Always','Always','Rishabh continues to grow in his playing - both musically and technically.  His obvious love for music is revealed through lunch practices with Ramanuj on music he finds or transcribes on Muse Score.  Rishabh\'s combined love for music and technology can easily intertwine through paid or open source music software that he has found. He can continue to challenge himself on reading rhythms and pitches with more accuracy but overall, he should keep up the excellent work!  ','2012-03-20 06:26:09','2012-03-20 06:26:09'),(487,1326,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Usually','Occasionally','Unacceptable','Usually','Aubrey works satisfactorily but is capable of greater effort and improvement.  Aubrey is an able performer, but  whose performance varies with interest. Aubrey  must have more self-discipline and the determination to improve the performance in order to progress towards meeting and exceeding the standards.','2012-03-20 06:27:11','2012-03-23 06:27:23'),(488,824,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Usually','Always','Usually','Always','Sam is progressing quickly on his trumpet playing.  He continues to play with accurate rhythms.  Occasionally he plays with inaccurate pitches but quickly remedies this by asking his neighboring trumpet players.  Sam is encouraged to ask questions when he does not understand and continue to work towards playing with accurate fingerings or pitches on his trumpet.  He can also work towards playing more musically by phrasing and playing with a more rounded tone quality.  Overall, Sam has grown quickly into an excellent trumpet player and should keep up the great work! ','2012-03-20 06:30:32','2012-03-20 06:30:32'),(489,300,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Always','Always','Always','Always','Sina\'s diligence and work ethic are obvious as she improves in her clarinet playing.  She continues to gain rhythmic and pitch accuracies as she practices as well.  Although Sina is faced with challenges at times, she perseveres and works through those musical challenges.  Keep working on the difficult, high notes and learn the fingerings, Sina.  You are on your way to becoming a fantastic, young clarinet player.  Keep up the excellent work! ','2012-03-20 06:32:54','2012-03-20 06:32:54'),(490,582,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Usually','Always','Always','Always','Sophie continues to grow and mature in her clarinet playing.  Occasionally she tangents from playing in class and is distracted by nearby friends.  However, her rhythmic and pitch accuracies are obviously due to her diligence in her practice time outside of class.  Sophie can keep challenging herself with playing higher pitches with fingering accuracies and excellent tone qualities.  Keep up the excellent work, Sophie! ','2012-03-20 06:34:56','2012-03-20 06:35:12'),(491,814,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Usually','Always','Always','Always','Tomas has done nothing but excel on his baritone horn.  Rarely is he distracted by his friends nearby and is always ready to answer questions in class with a smile and eagerness.  His boldness in sound while playing the baritone as well as playing with pitch and rhythmic accuracies are to be applauded.  Tomas has recently volunteered to also mentor a young grade five baritone horn student after school.  This will be another opportunity for Tomas to grow in his baritone horn playing.  Keep up the excellent work, Tomas!  ','2012-03-20 06:38:36','2012-03-20 06:38:36'),(492,1747,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Always','Always','Always','Always','William continues to play the tenor saxophone with rhythmic and pitch accuracies.  He would benefit from playing with more musicianship:  dynamics, articulations, phrasing and so forth.  Overall, William is doing a good job and should keep up the good work! ','2012-03-20 06:40:29','2012-03-20 06:40:29'),(493,1344,NULL,NULL,'Q3','Always','Always','Always','Always','Yema continues to seek out opportunities to challenge herself on her clarinet.  This quarter, she has quietly and steadily worked on playing the bass clarinet with rhythmic and pitch accuracies.  While there were challenges to playing the bass clarinet, she has done a fantastic job of seeking out help when needed and diligently practicing.  If nothing else, playing the bass clarinet will improve h